<p><strong>Tamil Bible Quiz Questions and Answers PDF: Test Your Scriptural Knowledge</strong></p>
<p>Engage in a compelling Bible quiz that tests your knowledge of the Tamil version of the Holy Scriptures. This article presents a selection of questions and answers, available in PDF format for your convenience.</p>
<p><strong>Paragraph 1: Genesis (創世記):</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Question: Who was the first man created by God in Genesis?</li>
<li>Answer: ஆதாம் (Adam)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Paragraph 2: Exodus (இஸ்ரவேலர் புத்தகம்):</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Question: What was the name of the Egyptian pharaoh who enslaved the Israelites?</li>
<li>Answer: பார்வோன் (Pharaoh)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Paragraph 3: Isaiah (ஏசாயா):</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Question: According to Isaiah 40:31, what will those who wait for the Lord experience?</li>
<li>Answer: அவர்கள் தங்கள் சக்தியைப் புதுப்பிப்பார்கள்.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Paragraph 4: Matthew (மத்தேயு):</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Question: In Matthew 6:9-13, what is the first line of the Lord's Prayer?</li>
<li>Answer: விண்ணகத் தந்தையே, உமது நாமம் பரிசுத்தமாக்கப்படுவாக</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Paragraph 5: Acts (அப்போஸ்தலர் நடபடிகள்):</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Question: Who was the first Christian martyr?</li>
<li>Answer: ஸ்தேவான் (Stephen)</li>
</ul>
